snippet: ROSENBERG--William, 71, of East Brunswick, NJ passed away on December 30, 2013. He is survived by his wife Andrea, three children and eight grandchildren. Services will be held Thursday, January 2, 2014 at AEMT, New Bruns-wick, NJ at 11am....
lead_paragraph: ROSENBERG--William, 71, of East Brunswick, NJ passed away on December 30, 2013. He is survived by his wife Andrea, three children and eight grandchildren. Services will be held Thursday, January 2, 2014 at AEMT, New Bruns-wick, NJ at 11am.
